<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٩٣٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/13865">‌يُونُسُ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3001">‌طَلْحَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">‌نَافِعٍ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">‌ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a>قَالَ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ: <span class="c2">«لَعَنَ اللهُ الْوَاصِلَةَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٦٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَالْمُسْتَوْصِلَةَ وَالْوَاشِمَةَ وَالْمُسْتَوْشِمَةَ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>